@axologic/cli

This package is a from-scratch, dependency-free reimplementation of the
component-installer workflow popularised by shadcn/ui. It is compatible with
the `components.json` configuration schema and the registry-item JSON schema
so that users familiar with shadcn feel at home.

No source code from the shadcn/ui CLI is included; the project is credited for
the design of the workflow and the configuration/registry schemas.

